$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 SIT {
  coords 1518.605 27.012 7941.246
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>PRELIMS</h2>"\
  "DTL: 05/01/1991, 0800hr, Al-Hadra, Kuwait."\
  "Weather: Clear, no forecast of change."\
  ""\
  "<h2>LORE</h2>"\
  "Coalition forces continue offensive operations into Kuwait as Iraqi units attempt to regroup and reinforce fragmented positions across the region. Intelligence reports indicate an Iraqi mechanised force is moving toward Al-Hadra with the intention of bypassing coalition lines and linking up with a sister company operating further north."\
  "British forces have been ordered to fight through the dense urban districts of the city and secure the northern highway before the reinforcements can break through. Iraqi defenders already positioned throughout Al-Hadra are expected to resist heavily, using the city itself to delay the advance and buy time for incoming forces."\
  "Control of the highway will determine whether the Iraqi reinforcements reach their objective — or are stopped inside the city."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 CS {
  coords 1518.605 27.012 7941.246
  m_sTitle "Comsig"
  m_sTextData "<h2>CALLSIGNS</h2>"\
  "• HQ - 41 | OC - 41A | PSG - 41B"\
  "• 1SEC - 41C"\
  "• 2SEC - 41D"\
  "• 3SEC - 41E"\
  "• 4SEC - 41F"\
  "• 5SEC (Sappers) - 41G"\
  ""\
  "<h2>FREQ/CHAN</h2>"\
  "• All callsigns - 48hz"\
  ""\
  "<h2>PASSWORDS</h2>"\
  "All can be changed at CO's discretion."\
  "• <b>Challenge:</b> Bounty | <b>Password:</b> Twix"\
  "• Running password: 12"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 EF {
  coords 1518.605 27.012 7941.246
  m_sTitle "Enemy forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>  "\
  "Enemy forces consist of regular Iraqi Army troops from Shako Battalion.  "\
  "Estimated enemy strength is approximately 25–30 personnel.  "\
  ""\
  "Enemy forces are spread throughout the dense urban area to our front. They maintain full freedom of movement within the city, though are currently contained by coalition cordon elements.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>  "\
  "• 1x dug-in BTR has been identified observing the main dual carriageway through our lane. Its role is to deny our movements along the road while keeping the route open for Iraqi movement and withdrawal without relying on movement through buildings."\
  "• The enemy holds the advantage of defence and is expected to remain in prepared positions awaiting the assault. There is no reason for them to conduct counter-attacks.  "\
  "• Expect multiple established fighting positions, fortified buildings, and pre-sighted engagement areas throughout the urban terrain.  "\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 FF {
  coords 1518.605 27.012 7941.246
  m_sTitle "Friendly forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>  "\
  "We are 1st Platoon, Delta Company, 3rd Battalion, Royal Regiment of Fusiliers.  "\
  "Currently located at our staging area, GRID: 040045"\
  "Our force consists of 41 personnel, with an additional 25 troops available to reinforce as we take casualties.  "\
  "They will be delivered to the flagpole at our staging area in waves every 60 seconds."\
  "- Our platoon sergeant should handle the reinforcements."\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>  "\
  "• Most personnel are equipped with optics compared to Iraqi forces who largely lack optical sights.  "\
  "• Attached sappers possess 1x large and 4x small demolition charges. These can be used to breach fortified positions or potentially collapse structures if employed effectively and combined."\
  " "\
  "<h2>SERVICE & SUPPORT</h2>  "\
  "• One support Land Rovers carrying additional ammunition, equipment, and supplies to rearm from during the fight."\
  "This includes also includes 4x extendable ladders."\
  "• An attached medic with an ambulance containing additional medical supplies and equipment."\
  "- Our platoon sergeant should plan aid post and resupply locations."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 MIS {
  coords 1518.605 27.012 7941.246
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2>  "\
  "We are to OCCUPY the highway northeast of our position in order to DISRUPT advancing Iraqi reinforcements before they passthrough in ETA 45mins."\
  ""\
  "<h2>MISSION DESCRIPTION</h2>  "\
  "Iraqi forces are expected to push through Al-Hadra from the southeast along the highway in an attempt to bypass coalition lines and link up with a sister company further north.  "\
  ""\
  "Our Platoon+ has been ordered to maintain a lane through the city and fight toward the highway alongside company elements. We are to occupy the route and prepare to disrupt the incoming enemy forces through the area."\
  "We have a small window of 45mins to occupy the highway otherwise we'll miss the passing Iraqi forces."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
}